Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.31,0:00:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.51,0:00:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.98,0:00:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.52,0:00:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.63,0:00:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.84,0:00:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.64,0:00:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.92,0:01:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.03,0:01:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.67,0:01:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.84,0:01:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[零式系統]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是把戰況裡出現的一切資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.05,0:01:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在即時運算後\N得出的龐大預測值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.05,0:01:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接反饋給駕駛員的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.42,0:01:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛艙系統的俗稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.46,0:01:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這系統甚至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.46,0:01:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會把駕駛員趕進極端狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.13,0:01:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實現完美的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.57,0:01:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果連自己的死也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.07,0:01:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.64,0:01:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在世界變得混沌的時代裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.18,0:01:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存在了令人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為最強兵器的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.15,0:02:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是飛翼零式和次代鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.32,0:02:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十七話\N[零式VS次代]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣一直飛去山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要及時趕到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.48,0:02:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人…我的敵人在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰略上失去優勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰術層面最大功效確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?增援還沒來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令，敵人的戰鬥力仍未滅弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.64,0:03:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開戰線的士兵增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在撤退比較好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!如果就此撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.99,0:03:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會成為貴族的笑柄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，對手是鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們才更要打倒那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.36,0:03:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,財團不認同鋼彈這名稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.96,0:03:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的第42 MD空降師團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會變成只是被一部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.64,0:03:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無名的機動戰士殲滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.11,0:03:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人機動戰士前來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰術層面處理完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續轉到戰略層面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.92,0:04:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用這部飛翼零式能戰到哪地步?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.12,0:04:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起敵人，問題是自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛翼零式嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥層面，目標確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.61,0:04:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.71,0:04:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.99,0:04:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算挑戰這部飛翼零式嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.61,0:05:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯\N你選擇了那機體是錯誤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!我要確認戰況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問零式吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.05,0:05:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰情如何?\N山克王國怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.19,0:06:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國崩潰了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來遲一步了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.77,0:06:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，這場戰鬥有何意義?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟有何意義?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.45,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你講得沒錯啊  零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧，我就做一名單純的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你的宿命之戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天就在這裡決一勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.67,0:06:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始終無法聯絡到第42 MD空降師團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.64,0:06:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?\N派MD登陸部隊增援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人機動戰士確定了有兩部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對付他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要投入十倍的戰鬥力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.80,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要多少奶和砂糖?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.60,0:07:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想迪爾麥優侯爵很快就會來到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳愈來愈懷念滅亡的祖國吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是從我的庭罷園裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,採摘茶葉而成的紅茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.89,0:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許不合妳口味\N但希望妳飲用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.36,0:07:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪爾麥優侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.82,0:07:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不須要這樣款待我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.09,0:07:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我向你們投降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.37,0:07:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是指妳適合被關進監牢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，妳錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們保護了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳一直渴望和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.98,0:08:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們過去也才支援妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，妳的周圍集結了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.89,0:08:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從前背叛OZ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和衛星的叛亂份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.03,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們踐踏了妳的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.63,0:08:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護妳的理想\N才救妳出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世人會把今次山克王國的紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.91,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理解成那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳向全世界宣佈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和科主義既崇高又美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到了很多人的共鳴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我們為了保護那主義戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.63,0:08:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事情應該無人會相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，他們會相信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為羅姆斐拉團會把它的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為財團的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.11,0:09:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做財團的代表?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我?\N沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.05,0:09:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.91,0:09:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團會藉著全面擁立妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而得到全世界的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.65,0:09:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們統一地球的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就會成為事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.06,0:09:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然\N這須要妳和我們的合作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳肯成為財團的代表吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，妳已經不是公主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就稱你為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.34,0:09:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在世界最高處的莉莉娜女王吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可以出賣為了和平而戰的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.85,0:09:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個地球上能得到的最高地位\N就在妳眼前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不須那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想毫不羞恥地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.96,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在被壓迫的人的悲傷之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳和我們不同的只是方法論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.70,0:10:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們和妳也渴望\N沒有戰鬥的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳慢慢考慮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為還有時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.42,0:10:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，請妳不要忘記這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在妳猶豫的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.29,0:10:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渴望和平的人會繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多人會繼續死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.68,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢!好慢啊!次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超越他的反應速度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛翼零式!讓我看見勝利吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一招決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工程效率提升了20%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工程即將完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.69,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星居民的大量增員果然有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.23,0:12:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是君主政治支配的好處啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這麼重要的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不須要甚麼自由平等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.61,0:13:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人講得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西迪茲，我回去月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.75,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，請包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.47,0:13:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來還在使用有人機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該有命令你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.47,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那些人員派去戰艦工作班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能浪費戰力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.81,0:13:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是叛變的戰力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你坐好，特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們究竟…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們從前被稱為特列斯派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.99,0:13:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但今後就稱為\N衛星的革命鬥士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,革命?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.60,0:14:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們並非想取特校你的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.34,0:14:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星居民不希望殺戮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.14,0:14:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你們停止壓迫就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.25,0:14:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是熱狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羊已經走進欄裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[月亮女神革命]開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的是甚麼爆炸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.09,0:14:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經佔領這基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.63,0:14:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止無謂的反抗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是甚麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是衛星的革命鬥士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.91,0:14:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[白色獠牙]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的同胞們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們站起來的時候終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以來壓迫我們的茲巴洛夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在被我們的同志關起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.65,0:14:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經不須要再服從任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球貪婪地從我們身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奪去大量的勞力和資源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.06,0:15:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我們本來應該是平等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不用受任何人支配的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來吧，為了衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.47,0:15:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起建立宇宙的和平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.17,0:15:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於出手了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.61,0:15:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星又會跑進亂七八糟的戰爭裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.18,0:15:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人真笨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.12,0:15:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們為何不殺我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.09,0:15:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有利用價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你今後在\N各個衛星的傳媒上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宣佈戰敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而處決你方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.40,0:15:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想待居民\N衷心希望時才執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N那種做法和OZ沒有分別啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切是從你們身上學回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.48,0:15:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,口吻十足特列斯的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.25,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別追!他逃不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這基地是我們的地盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.60,0:16:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的叛亂份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.30,0:16:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們以為我已經束手無策了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.17,0:16:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的MD\N會粉碎你們的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特攻隊叫首領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基地周圍沒反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首領，MD啟動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在於北面閘門交戰中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.49,0:16:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲巴洛夫嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.58,0:16:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了\N以這種裝備毫無還手之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個宇宙希望戰鬥的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有邪惡意志的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都要全部消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!我們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廢話少講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈不是衛星的自己人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的MD不會戰敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最終成為勝利者的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.07,0:17:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我和我的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.25,0:18:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧，我的MD是無敵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.59,0:18:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個宇宙毫無敵手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是無敵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是貫徹我的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.08,0:18:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是月球基地鎮壓部隊來的報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.38,0:18:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的反抗已經鎮壓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，鋼彈出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.12,0:18:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，好像是05的改良型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲巴洛夫怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像被捲入那場戰鬥中死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.66,0:18:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?  沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我們的計劃怎麼辦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[月亮女神革命]只是剛剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.21,0:19:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這艘艦完成後，革命就會成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們看來都被機械擺佈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次代告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我選擇的路上的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也認為那沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.83,0:19:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.94,0:19:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在北面B地點的海灣戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.18,0:19:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出動所有MD殲滅他們!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.25,0:19:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD登陸預定時間0450
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有何打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.39,0:19:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我駕駛飛翼零式進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去消滅海上的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部鋼彈怎樣處置?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.46,0:20:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是特列斯製造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能理解他的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的確會把次代交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.35,0:20:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來打算選擇和你不同的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在讓我使用這部次代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.37,0:21:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.14,0:21:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.46,0:21:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你轉告迪爾麥優侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.20,0:21:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特答應他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為羅姆斐拉財團的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.71,0:21:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就行了呢\N莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.16,0:22:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.61,0:22:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.61,0:22:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.61,0:22:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.61,0:22:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.11,0:22:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.61,0:23:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.11,0:23:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.61,0:23:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.61,0:23:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.81,0:23:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武裝起來的衛星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.34,0:23:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自稱[白色獠牙]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.74,0:23:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸續攻陷OZ在宇宙駐守的重鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.01,0:23:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那漩渦裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.88,0:23:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾和諾茵\N繼續找尋鋼彈駕駛員
